1. You should know every single word about your notebook
2. She might ask why used this and not this?? {for example why onehot and not label encode}
3. All the models you have defined, you should know every hyperparameter reason too. {for example why used logloss as evalmetric or why used a certain threshold value}
4. for preprocessing the question were similar to other's responses

That was it for me!

1. Go through explaining your entire notebook. {15-20mins}
2. How does Logistic Regression works? {30secs}
3. What is One-Hot-Encoding? Give an example. {30 secs}
4. Is Hyperparameter Tuning and Pipelining present or not. {5secs}

Good Luck for your Viva-2!! {15secs}

Present THE notebook! {20mins}
